import React from 'react'
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import Stack from 'react-bootstrap/Stack';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';


const BookFilter = (props) => {

return (
    <Container>
    <Stack direction="horizontal" gap={3}>
        <label  htmlFor="isbn" className="form-label">Try AI filter assitant</label>
        <Form.Control className="me-auto" placeholder="What dou you search for?" />
        <Button variant="primary">Try AI</Button>
    </Stack>

            <Stack>
                <Col>
                <label htmlFor="author" className="form-label">try old way</label>
                <input className="form-control" type="text"
                id="author"
                value=""
                required
                />
                </Col>
                <Col>
            <button type="button" className="btn btn-primary">Try old way</button>
                </Col>
            </Stack>
    </Container>
    )
}

export default BookFilter
